# The built dashboard bundle is COMMITTED. The ops console is part of the
# product and is ALWAYS embedded in the `aion-server`/`aion` binary (rust_embed
# over this directory, no cargo feature). A plain `cargo build` / `cargo install`
# therefore ships the real UI at `/`.
#
# Regenerate this bundle with `cargo xtask build-dashboard` and commit the
# result. CI's `cargo xtask verify-dashboard` fails if the committed bundle is
# stale against a clean rebuild of the dashboard source.
#
# We commit index.html, assets/**, and favicon.svg. Only stray sourcemaps are
# ignored as a belt-and-braces guard against accidental .map bloat (the Vite
# config builds with sourcemap: false, so none should appear).
*.map
